{"tid":2055154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣大範圍解除防疫措施","createTime":"2020-06-07T17:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T19:26:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"414b9298e977e98ff529c2020b8ab099624987da","tid":2055154,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"台灣大範圍解除防疫措施<br />\n2020-06-07 HKT 20:10<br />\n<br />\n台灣大範圍解除防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n流行疫情指揮中心表示，台灣已連續8周未出現本土感染病例，當局將解除數項主要防疫措施，包括，日常和休閒活動不再控制人數；乘坐公共交通工具的限制也陸續解除；台鐵和高鐵恢復列車上食品供應，因應疫情延期的宗教活動和服務也將逐步恢復。<br />\n<br />\n台北故宮博物院昨日已取消進場人數限制，訪客無須戴口罩入內。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530706-20200607.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530706-20200607.htm&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=5cd1b58f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530706-20200607.htm&h=8d02614f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530706-20200607.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣堅係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"19f0ea6ea3615c7385d4260ecf70b8d0f0e76e87","tid":2055154,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得台灣要小心中国<br />\n<br />\n尤其相信生化戰陰謀論"},{"pid":"75a8934be0922384e5efb3fc806f4a71ecac343b","tid":2055154,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"要繼續封中國關，小心支那第二波武統"},{"pid":"432f4b854f753dc9b826073f8112211eda614df4","tid":2055154,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19f0ea6ea3615c7385d4260ecf70b8d0f0e76e87","tid":2055154,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得台灣要小心中国<br />\n<br />\n